            <lg xml:id="TK1316">
<l>uḷḷiṉē meṉṟīrmaṟ ṟemmaṟantī reṉṟemmaip</l>
<l>pullāḷ pulattak kaṉaḷ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When I said I had remembered her, she said I had forgotten her and relaxing her embrace, began to feign dislike.</l>
            </lg>
